    <item>
      <title>高级官员称中国刺激计划旨在促进消费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/china-s-stimulus-aims-to-boost-consumption-top-official-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部副部长廖岷表示，中国近期推出的刺激政策主要围绕扩大内需和实现国家年度增长目标。投资者正在等待全国人大会议公布中国政府关键财政刺激方案的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/china-s-stimulus-aims-to-boost-consumption-top-official-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 03:31:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>达美航空因“灾难性”软件故障起诉 CrowdStrike</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/delta-sues-crowdstrike-over-catastrophic-software-glitch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[达美航空公司 (Delta Air Lines Inc.) 起诉网络安全公司 CrowdStrike Holdings Inc.，原因是今年夏天一次“灾难性”的软件更新造成了混乱，导致全球数百万台计算机瘫痪，并导致该航空公司的大部分客机停飞。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/delta-sues-crowdstrike-over-catastrophic-software-glitch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 02:48:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩洛哥计划在 2026 年放松与欧元的货币挂钩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/morocco-aims-to-loosen-currency-peg-to-euro-dollar-in-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩洛哥央行行长在接受采访时表示，摩洛哥计划在 2026 年放松汇率制度，恢复在疫情期间中止的渐进式改革进程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/morocco-aims-to-loosen-currency-peg-to-euro-dollar-in-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 00:20:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对中国股市而言，刺激措施比美国大选更重要</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/stimulus-matters-more-than-us-election-for-chinese-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[多年来已习惯中美贸易争端的投资者似乎愿意冒着美国总统大选后关税进一步上调的风险，并青睐中国资产，押注美国将出台更多刺激措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-26/stimulus-matters-more-than-us-election-for-chinese-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 26 Oct 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
